{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"MILESTONE: all 13 remediation changes (202-214) MERGED to main via Gerrit (two-bot gate: LLM-Review + Verified/CI), plus the earlier Critical has_llm_steps fix (188). One CI hiccup handled mid-flight: change 211 (Fix A) failed the mypy gate — a type-var issue in the new blocking-finding code (my gap: ran make lint but not make typecheck on the batch); fixed by str-coercing the file list, amended into 211, re-verified (mypy 246 files clean), re-pushed, merged. Change 189 (child-closure docs) re-pushed onto main-with-.gitleaks.toml: its LLM-Review block CLEARED (now +1) — end-to-end validation that the Fix A rendering bug + Fix B gitleaks allowlist resolved the false -1/0-findings vote. 189 CI finishing. Remaining epic children: 13/14/15/9.3 (config/reconcile splits, shared-helper sweep, dir reorg, facade reroute) — CHECKPOINTED for a post-release maintenance pass."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783069431088334001,"uuid":"4fef66c2-4d08-40c7-a40b-00b281fbce40"}